summary: AN ORDINANCE designating the unnamed street commencing at the intersection of Meridian Avenue North and North 103rd Street and extending southwesterly to its intersection with Burke Avenue North and North 100th Street as College Way North, changing the name of that portion of Burke Avenue North as existing between North 100th Street and North 95th Street to College Way North, and designating a proposed street running southwesterly from the intersection of Burke Avenue North and North 95th Street to the intersection of Wallingford Avenue North and North 92nd Street, at the time of City acquisition of right of way, as College Way North.
